      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Washington Water Power COM\npany has applied to the city council\nfor the renewal of the franchise\ngranting 1t the right to construct\nand operate a system of electric rail-\nways, commencing at the intersection\nof Front avenue and the Northern\nPacific tracks, west to Post street\nand thence north to the c. & c. mills\nfor the purpose of carrying cereals\nand the products OF cereals.\n\n\nThe line in question is already\nbuilt and is being operated for the\npurposes asked for."
